>Description:
DrScheme colors #px"foo" red instead of green.
The reason is that the lexer doesn't know the #px-syntax.

Patch:

  In /collects/syntax-color/scheme-lexer.ss
  replace the 3 occurences of

      "#rx"

  with

      (:or "#rx" "#px")
